{"tid":965453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"猥褻男「騷擾+戲弄」！印度女把人綁樹上　狠斷他「命根子」給教訓","createTime":"2019-01-02T05:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T13:11:50.000Z","uid":212399,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f0d628411f279500bcca1fa18a37f1048ef1ee2e","tid":965453,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:14:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3804/3804709.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3804%2F3804709.jpg&h=653559c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲女子因為遭受騷擾跟戲弄，將男子陰莖砍斷。（圖／翻攝自太陽報）<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n印度孟買一名女子長期受到一名30歲男子的騷擾跟戲弄，為了要教訓這名男子，她夥同2名朋友，把人引誘到一個偏僻的地方綁在樹上，並將男子的「生殖器」砍下後逃離現場。<br />\n根據外媒報導，這起事件發生在印度孟買附近的棟比夫利（Dombivali），該名涉案女子的姓名未被公開，她告訴調查人員，遭到攻擊的30歲男子曾經騷擾跟戲弄過她，儘管她多次「警告」，但男子仍持續做出一樣的行為，她已經受夠了這種對待，所以決定給這人「上一課」。<br />\n女子在2名朋友的協助之下，將男子引誘到鐵路附近一處偏僻的地方，3人先是壓倒並毆打該名男子，隨後將人綁在樹幹上用武器將其的生殖器砍掉；當地居民在發現滿身是傷的男子後報警，並將人緊急送醫。<br />\n報導中指出，男子的傷勢相當嚴重，治療仍在進行當中；而犯案女子及其共犯也已經遭到警方逮捕，預計在近日出庭接受審判。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190102/1345644.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190102%2F1345644.htm&d=8bpNXnFkE57gNuvy2jcr2SwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=9676cea2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190102/1345644.htm</a>"},{"pid":"aad9b932cfdab63a1efc8499203eb0b35b2e4bc1","tid":965453,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4699092b523f95541ce2d83f04503dc8c18600","tid":965453,"uid":55045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:21:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ff17fa412345d9f8af5b638ee27d78df121d0c","tid":965453,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:25:32.000Z","msg":"用什麼武器?"},{"pid":"b84e47d9ff3aa63f66255baaf79e3cac6c5e4ba4","tid":965453,"uid":64601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c0ff17fa412345d9f8af5b638ee27d78df121d0c","tid":965453,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:25:32.000Z","msg":"用什麼武器?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T13:11:50.000Z","msg":"指甲鋏"}]}